![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1615418885978-W9NVJXEHXDTXSX4ICTRI/168.jpg?format=original)

Oh MCU how we have missed you! Just like old friends meeting together for the first time in a long time it turns out we have ALOT to be filled in on when it comes to our favorite Avenging Couple of Wanda Maximoff and the Vision. Last we saw of these two, Vision was brutally neutralized by the Mad Titan Thanos, and Wanda was mourning her lost love after Avengers Endgame. How exactly has the Vision returned? What is the mental state of Wanda Maximoff one of the most tragic figures in the Marvel Cinematic Universe? Who the HELL is RALPH BOHNER?! Some but not all of these questions will be answered as we review Marvel's masterclass in mental health and grief counseling; **WandaVision!**

**Please** leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](../episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
